PtexReader: mark getEntry() as an exported symbol

ptexinfo relies on being able to query using getEntry() through
an inlined call to getValue().

Expose the getEntry() symbols to allow ptxinfo to be built when
using shared libraries only.

Closes #67

commit.message:
Merge pull request #68 from anderslanglands/main

* anderslanglands/main:
  replace pkgconfig with find_package
  remove inaccurate comment
  Use find_package() for zlib instead of pkg-config

Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
replace pkgconfig with find_package
remove inaccurate comment

Use find_package() for zlib instead of pkg-config

pkg-config is not available on windows (and finding, building and installing it is tricky). The native FindZLIB.cmake works just fine and is used by mahy other projects.

tests: use the binary location for test executables

generator expression to access the executable.

Remove it since it's no longer needed.
